  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/4> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/PoliticalIntrigue>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The film centers on political maneuvering, trade disputes, and secret agendas." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/4> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Mentorship>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The relationship between Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn and his apprentice Obi-Wan Kenobi is central." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/5> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/PoliticalIntrigue>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The film centers on Senate debates, separatist movements, and manipulation behind the scenes." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/5> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Betrayal>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "Count Dooku's actions and the creation of the clone army involve deception and hidden agendas." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/6> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Betrayal>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The film centers on Anakin's betrayal of the Jedi and the Republic." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/6> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/PoliticalIntrigue>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The kidnapping of Palpatine and the Republic's collapse highlight intrigue." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/2> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/EmpireVsRebellion>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The film centers on the ongoing conflict between the Empire and the Rebellion." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/2> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Survival>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The Rebels struggle to survive after being driven from their base by the Empire." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/3> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/EmpireVsRebellion>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The film centers on the struggle between the Rebel Alliance and the Empire." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/3> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Redemption>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "Key characters, especially Darth Vader, face opportunities for redemption." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/1> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/EmpireVsRebellion>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The film centers on the conflict between the oppressive Empire and the Rebels." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/1> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Survival>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The Rebels fight to survive against the Empire's overwhelming power." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/7> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/EmpireVsRebellion>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The First Order (successor to the Empire) opposes the Resistance and Republic." .
  
  <<<https://swapi.co/resource/film/7> <http://www.example.com/theme> <http://www.example.com/Survival>>>
    <http://www.example.com/reason> "The Resistance struggles to survive against the rising threat of the First Order." .
}
